{
  "texts": [
    "This paper reviews ML/DL-based solutions for the security of IoT.",
    "According to the studies and research done in this field, we can boldly recommend graph neural networks to detect attacks.",
    "GNN can be mixed with other data set classifiers to increase the accuracy of the operation significantly.",
    "In the meantime, the AdaBoost device significantly increases the overall accuracy in voting and classifiers.",
    "SGDM and ADAM can be used to train the weight of classifications."
  ]
}